## Chaining All Three: CLI Command Design

Suggested new commands to add to `brief`:

```
brief full "ai sales roleplay"
  → runs: generate brief → generate blog → generate banner
  → saves all three to /output/{slug}/brief.md, blog.md, banner.svg

brief blog "ai sales roleplay"
  → requires brief already generated OR generates one first
  → saves blog to /output/{slug}/blog.md

brief banner "ai sales roleplay"
  → requires blog already generated
  → extracts title + keyword from blog frontmatter
  → saves SVG to /output/{slug}/banner.svg
```

